         <meta.schema plugin="org.palladiosimulator.editors.sirius.custom.style" id="/org.palladiosimulator.editors.sirius.custom.style.node.image" name="Nodes Image"/>
      </appInfo>
      <documentation>
         Extension for nodes graphic style : enable rotatable images.
Two ways :
- with one image (top) : take this image for north side and rotate it (90° for east/right side, 180° for south/bottom side, 270° for west/left side)
- with 4 images : display the right image on each side (top at north, right at east, bottom at south and right at west)
      </documentation>
   </annotation>

